HEADWORD: Nose around
<hw>Nose around</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to look around
or search, especially where one has no authority to do so; to pry; to be
nosy. Same as <er>nose{2}</er>, <pos>v. i.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
